OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine
OL,7,Fbut cloud along eastern coasts
OL,8,Fgradually edging inland tonight with
OL,9,Fsome mist, but the Trossachs and most
OL,10,Fof highland Perthshire staying clear,
OL,11,Fand turning chilly there.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FLow cloud ineast burning
OL,14,Fback to coast once again where patches
OL,15,Fmay linger, otherwise long spells of
OL,16,Funbroken sunshine. Very warm in west,
OL,17,Fcoastal districts cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
